Program: Discovery
Title: Helping children with brain damage
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwxl
Last Broadcast Date: 21 July 1997
Helping brain damaged children to remember. How children are benefiting from new findings about the role of the hippocampus and memory. Also in the programme how did vertebrates get their back bones and could there be water on the Sun? Presenter: Martin Redfern.